## ADsurdity: Privacy policy
The ADsurdity app is purely to show how ads work in mobile apps and to do so using Kotlin and Jetpack Compose.

### Data collected by the app
The app does not collect user data except for diagnostic or debuggin purposes provided by Firebase and Crashlytics.

### Explanation of permissions requested in the app
The app only needs permissions for network/internet access and to get the ad id information.
| Permission | Why it is required |
| :---: | --- |
| `android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE` | Needed to connect to the AdMob API for downloading ads |
| `android.permission.INTERNET` | Needed to connect to the AdMob API for downloading ads |
| `com.google.android.gms.permission.AD_ID` | Needed to connect to verify the ads are associated with my AdMob account |
